Google Sheets: Suggested Columns for Each Sheet
1. Users
Column Name	Type	Description
id	String	Unique user ID (e.g., U001)
name	String	Moderator/Admin name
email	String	Login email
password_hash	String	Hashed password (for JWT login)
mobile_number	String	Moderator phone
telegram_chat_id	String	For Telegram notifications
bot_token	String	Per-user Telegram Bot token
role	Enum	Admin, Moderator
status	Enum	Active, Inactive

2. Products
Column Name	Type	Description
id	String	Product ID (e.g., P001)
name	String	Product name
sales_price	Decimal	Sale price in BDT
production_price	Decimal	Cost of production
discount_price	Decimal	Optional discount
product_image_url	String	ImgBB URL
status	Enum	Active, Inactive

3. Orders
Column Name	Type	Description
order_id	String	NF-001, NF-002 auto-generated
customer_name	String	
mobile_number	String	
email	String	Optional
address	Text	
moderator_id	String	Ref to Users id
notes	Text	Optional
product_id	String	Ref to Products id
order_source	Enum	Messenger, Call, WhatsApp
fraud_result	JSON/Text	Fraud API response
delivery_charge	Decimal	
status	Enum	Pending-Moderator, Delivered, etc.
created_at	DateTime	
updated_at	DateTime	
steadfast_tracking_id	String	After successful order

4. FollowUps
Column Name	Type	Description
followup_id	String	Unique ID (e.g., F001)
order_id	String	Ref to Orders
followup_date	Date	Date to remind
notes	Text	Follow-up notes
status	Enum	Pending, Completed

5. Tasks
Column Name	Type	Description
task_id	String	Task ID (e.g., T001)
order_id	String	Ref to Orders
task_details	Text	
assigned_to	String	Ref to Users
status	Enum	Pending, In Progress, Completed
created_at	DateTime	
due_date	DateTime	
priority	Enum	Low, Medium, High
